\b Appendix: How to Run on Another PC (Windows)\b0\par
\pard\li720\sa80
1) Install prerequisites: Node.js 18+, Python 3.11+, Git\par
2) Backend (Django):\par
\pard\li1080\sa60
\'95 Create and activate a virtualenv\par
\'95 Install from \f1 backend\\requirements.txt\f0\par
\'95 Run migrations: \f1 python backend\\manage.py migrate\f0\par
\'95 Start server: \f1 python backend\\manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000\f0\par
\pard\li720\sa60
3) Frontend (Vite):\par
\pard\li1080\sa60
\'95 From \f1 frontend\f0: \f1 npm install\f0 then \f1 npm run dev\f0 (note the dev URL and port)\par
\'95 Ensure \f1 VITE_API_BASE\f0 points to the backend URL if needed\par
\pard\li720\sa60
4) Open the frontend dev URL in a browser, sign up/login, and use the app.\par
\pard\sa200

